      </ul>
    </nav>
  </header>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
    <p>We are here to assist you with any questions or help you arrange your purchases. Contact either of us directly:</p>
    
    <div class="contact-card">
      <div class="icon">
